---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - MarkdownMaster"
  description="MarkdownMaster privacy policy. We do not collect personal data. Read about how we protect your privacy."
  canonical="https://markdownmaster.site/privacy/"
>
  <style>
    .page-wrap { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .page-wrap h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .page-wrap h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem; color: var(--accent); }
    .page-wrap p { color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .page-wrap ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .page-wrap li { margin: 0.3rem 0; }
  </style>

  <div class="page-wrap">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>MarkdownMaster is a client-side application. Your documents and content are never sent to our servers. All processing happens entirely in your browser.</p>
    <p>We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> - for typography. Google may collect usage data as described in their privacy policy.</li>
      <li><strong>jsDelivr CDN</strong> - to serve the marked.js library. jsDelivr may log standard HTTP request data.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> - as our hosting and CDN provider. Cloudflare may collect standard web server logs.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>MarkdownMaster does not use cookies. No tracking, analytics, or advertising cookies are employed.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since all data processing happens client-side in your browser, there is no data transmission or storage risk related to your document content.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out via our GitHub repository.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
